{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "HowTo",
  "name": "[How to Do Something - Primary Keyword]",
  "description": "[Brief overview of what will be accomplished - 150 characters]",
  "image": {
    "@type": "ImageObject",
    "url": "[https://yourdomain.com/images/howto-image.jpg]",
    "height": 406,
    "width": 305
  },
  "estimatedCost": {
    "@type": "MonetaryAmount",
    "currency": "USD",
    "value": "0"
  },
  "supply": [
    {
      "@type": "HowToSupply",
      "name": "[Supply or Tool 1]"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToSupply",
      "name": "[Supply or Tool 2]"
    }
  ],
  "tool": [
    {
      "@type": "HowToTool",
      "name": "[Tool or Software 1]"
    }
  ],
  "step": [
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "position": 1,
      "name": "[Step 1 Title]",
      "text": "[Detailed instruction for step 1. Be specific and actionable. Include any warnings or tips.]",
      "image": "[https://yourdomain.com/images/step1.jpg]",
      "url": "[https://yourdomain.com/article#step1]"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "position": 2,
      "name": "[Step 2 Title]",
      "text": "[Detailed instruction for step 2.]",
      "image": "[https://yourdomain.com/images/step2.jpg]",
      "url": "[https://yourdomain.com/article#step2]"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "position": 3,
      "name": "[Step 3 Title]",
      "text": "[Detailed instruction for step 3.]",
      "image": "[https://yourdomain.com/images/step3.jpg]",
      "url": "[https://yourdomain.com/article#step3]"
    }
  ],
  "totalTime": "PT30M",
  "video": {
    "@type": "VideoObject",
    "name": "[Video Title]",
    "description": "[Video description]",
    "thumbnailUrl": "[https://yourdomain.com/images/video-thumbnail.jpg]",
    "contentUrl": "[https://yourdomain.com/videos/howto.mp4]",
    "uploadDate": "[2025-01-15T10:00:00Z]"
  }
}

/*
USAGE NOTES:

1. HowTo Schema Benefits:
   - Voice search optimized (Google Assistant, Alexa)
   - Step-by-step rich results in Google
   - Featured in Google Discover
   - High AI citation probability
   - Mobile-friendly display

2. Duration Format (ISO 8601):
   - PT30M = 30 minutes
   - PT1H = 1 hour
   - PT2H30M = 2 hours 30 minutes
   - PT45S = 45 seconds
   - P1D = 1 day

3. Step Requirements:
   - Minimum 2 steps
   - Each step needs: position, name, text
   - Include images when possible
   - Link to page sections (#step1, #step2)
   - Keep text actionable and clear

4. Images:
   - Main image: 305Ã—406px (vertical orientation)
   - Step images: Any size, but consistent
   - Use actual screenshots or photos
   - Compress for fast loading

5. Supply vs Tool:
   - Supply: Consumable items (ingredients, materials)
   - Tool: Reusable items (software, equipment)
   - Optional but recommended for completeness

6. Cost:
   - Use "$0" for free methods
   - Or: "currency": "USD", "value": "50"
   - Can use range: "minValue": "20", "maxValue": "50"

VOICE SEARCH OPTIMIZATION:

Google Assistant reads:
1. HowTo name
2. Total time
3. Each step in order
4. Supplies/tools needed

Optimization tips:
- Use natural language in step names
- Keep step text concise (2-3 sentences)
- Include time estimates per step if long
- Use action verbs (Create, Add, Configure, Test)

EXAMPLES:

Technical Tutorial:
"name": "How to Optimize Website for AI Search Engines"
"totalTime": "PT2H"
"step": [
  {
    "position": 1,
    "name": "Add FAQ Schema",
    "text": "Create JSON-LD FAQ schema with 3-5 common questions. Place in <head> or before </body>."
  }
]

Medical Process:
"name": "How to Interpret Longevity Biomarker Results"
"totalTime": "PT15M"
"step": [
  {
    "position": 1,
    "name": "Compare to Optimal Ranges",
    "text": "Check LDL cholesterol against optimal target of <70 mg/dL, not standard lab reference of 100 mg/dL."
  }
]

Business Process:
"name": "How to Create Effective Client Proposals"
"totalTime": "PT1H30M"
"supply": ["Client requirements document", "Company template"]
"tool": ["Microsoft Word", "Google Docs"]

AI PLATFORM BENEFITS:

ChatGPT:
- Summarizes process steps
- Extracts actionable instructions
- Cites tutorial content
- Prefers structured how-to format

Perplexity:
- Lists step-by-step instructions
- Shows time estimates
- Links to original guide
- Displays supply/tool lists

Claude:
- Validates step logic
- Checks completeness
- Verifies actionability
- Prefers clear sequencing

Gemini:
- Integrates with Google Discover
- Shows in voice search results
- Displays rich snippets
- Prioritizes mobile experience

PLACEMENT:
Add to page with how-to content:
<script type="application/ld+json">
[PASTE JSON HERE]
</script>

TESTING:
- Google Rich Results Test: https://search.google.com/test/rich-results
- Test voice: "Hey Google, how to [your topic]"
- Check mobile display
- Verify step images load
*/
